    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/ywhwyf-mp/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_STATIC&editorId=626145269997634099&sectionId=626145270047965747)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"ggkQrrJalZ4_text","label":"ggkQrrJalZ4_text","default":"Your Questions, Answered"},{"type":"html","id":"ggsVBR1eUYD_childItem_0","label":"ggsVBR1eUYD_childItem_0","default":"<p>How often should I use the Bio-Collagen mask?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggsVBR1eUYD_childItem_1","label":"ggsVBR1eUYD_childItem_1","default":"<p>Why does the mask turn clear?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggsVBR1eUYD_childItem_2","label":"ggsVBR1eUYD_childItem_2","default":"<p>Do I need to wash my face after removing the mask?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggsVBR1eUYD_childItem_3","label":"ggsVBR1eUYD_childItem_3","default":"<p>Can I use different Nifora masks in the same week?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggsVBR1eUYD_childItem_4","label":"ggsVBR1eUYD_childItem_4","default":"<p>What should I do if the mask doesn’t stick well?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggsVBR1eUYD_childItem_5","label":"ggsVBR1eUYD_childItem_5","default":"<p>What ingredients are in this?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggsVBR1eUYD_childItem_6","label":"ggsVBR1eUYD_childItem_6","default":"<p>&nbsp;Is this vegan and cruelty-free?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggsVBR1eUYD_childItem_7","label":"ggsVBR1eUYD_childItem_7","default":"<p>Do I need to sit still for 3–4 hours to get the best results?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggsVBR1eUYD_childItem_8","label":"ggsVBR1eUYD_childItem_8","default":"<p>Doesn’t collagen come from within? How can this penetrate the skin?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggsVBR1eUYD_childItem_9","label":"ggsVBR1eUYD_childItem_9","default":"<p>Can the same mask be used more than once?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggsVBR1eUYD_childItem_10","label":"ggsVBR1eUYD_childItem_10","default":"<p>&nbsp;How long do the effects last after using the mask?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggsVBR1eUYD_childItem_11","label":"ggsVBR1eUYD_childItem_11","default":"<p>How do I use the Mask?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggsVBR1eUYD_childItem_12","label":"ggsVBR1eUYD_childItem_12","default":"<p>How many masks come in a pack?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggsVBR1eUYD_childItem_13","label":"ggsVBR1eUYD_childItem_13","default":"<p>How often &amp; how long should I use it?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggsVBR1eUYD_childItem_14","label":"ggsVBR1eUYD_childItem_14","default":"<p>Can I use the mask alongside my other skincare products?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggsVBR1eUYD_childItem_15","label":"ggsVBR1eUYD_childItem_15","default":"<p>Can I use it for sensitive skin?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggsVBR1eUYD_childItem_16","label":"ggsVBR1eUYD_childItem_16","default":"<p>Should I wash my face after using the mask?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggsVBR1eUYD_childItem_17","label":"ggsVBR1eUYD_childItem_17","default":"<p>100% Money back-guarantee?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggsVBR1eUYD_childItem_18","label":"ggsVBR1eUYD_childItem_18","default":"<p>What are the delivery times?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gzpdQTHjCqz_text","label":"gzpdQTHjCqz_text","default":"<p>For best results, we recommend using it 1-2 times per week to maintain optimal hydration and glow.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gbPuuVkVI2x_text","label":"gbPuuVkVI2x_text","default":"<p>The mask turns transparent as your skin absorbs the collagen serum. It's a visual sign that the mask has delivered its potent ingredients and the process is complete!</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gWqm04AkycM_text","label":"gWqm04AkycM_text","default":"<p>No, and please don't! The leftover essence is packed with nutrients. Gently pat it into your skin to receive the full benefits.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gfTC_331ERb_text","label":"gfTC_331ERb_text","default":"<p>Absolutely! We highly recommend it. For example, use our Bio-Collagen mask for deep hydration on Sunday, and our Vitamin C Radiance mask mid-week for a brightening boost. It’s the best way to give your skin everything it needs.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggKOJHDnWof_text","label":"ggKOJHDnWof_text","default":"<p>For best adherence, we recommend applying the mask to freshly cleansed, slightly damp skin. Take a moment to smooth it out gently, pressing down around the contours of your face. If needed, you can lay back and relax while it works its magic — the extra time also allows for deeper absorption. Some slip is natural due to the serum-rich formula, but that’s part of what makes it so effective at delivering moisture.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggyJVTCj59w_text","label":"ggyJVTCj59w_text","default":"<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong>Our Bio-Collagen Mask is formulated with skin-supportive ingredients designed to deliver deep hydration and visible firmness. Key ingredients include:</p><ul><li><strong>Hydrolyzed fish collagen (from salmon)</strong> – known for its smaller molecular size, making it easier for the skin to absorb. It helps support elasticity, smoothness, and firmness, especially in aging or dehydrated skin.<br>&nbsp;</li><li><strong>Niacinamide</strong> – helps brighten skin and even out tone.<br>&nbsp;</li><li><strong>Hyaluronic acid</strong> – provides intense, long-lasting hydration and plumping.<br>&nbsp;</li><li><strong>Peptides</strong> – support collagen production and improve overall skin resilience.<br>&nbsp;</li></ul><p>The mask’s <strong>hydrogel base</strong> allows for slow-release absorption, helping the skin drink in every ingredient — not just sit on the surface.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gglkOtUz4yY_text","label":"gglkOtUz4yY_text","default":"<p>We’re proud to say our mask is <strong>cruelty-free</strong> — absolutely no animal testing is involved at any stage of formulation or production.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>While it does contain <strong>hydrolyzed collagen</strong>, which is not plant-derived, we source it responsibly from marine ingredients. We know terms like “vegan collagen” can be confusing — and while some plant-based ingredients can help support collagen production, <strong>true collagen itself can only come from fish-based sources.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>That said, we’re always exploring more sustainable innovations while staying committed to delivering results — and kindness — through skincare.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggqNJ6BYFRR_text","label":"ggqNJ6BYFRR_text","default":"<p>Not at all! The mask is designed to move with you — most of our customers wear it while winding down for the night, whether that’s reading, watching TV, or getting ready for bed.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>In fact, <strong>78% of users wear the mask while they sleep</strong>, and many report <strong>up to 24% better hydration and visible skin smoothness</strong> when used overnight. The longer it stays on, the more time your skin has to soak in the benefits — all while you rest.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg4JkvcRc4w_text","label":"gg4JkvcRc4w_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16px;\">You’re absolutely right — collagen is produced naturally in the body, but production slows with age. Our mask uses </span><strong>hydrolyzed marine collagen</strong><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16px;\">, which is broken down into smaller peptides that are better able to </span><strong>absorb into the upper layers of the skin</strong><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16px;\">. It’s not about replacing collagen deep inside — it’s about supporting the skin’s structure, hydration, and visible bounce from the outside in.</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggmsse_m7JD_text","label":"ggmsse_m7JD_text","default":"<p>We don’t recommend reusing the mask. It’s designed as a single-use treatment to maintain hygiene and ensure maximum potency of the ingredients. Once used, the mask has already released most of its actives into your skin.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggwltw_cQZy_text","label":"ggwltw_cQZy_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16px;\">You’ll typically notice </span><strong>immediate hydration and visible plumpness</strong><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16px;\"> right after use. With weekly application, many customers see more long-term improvements in firmness and glow. Think of it as part of your ongoing skincare ritual, not just a one-time fix.</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggTmvsFWgsN_text","label":"ggTmvsFWgsN_text","default":"<p>🧴 <strong>Evening Routine:</strong> Cleanse and tone your face, ensuring your skin is free from oil and creams.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>🎭 <strong>Application:</strong> Start with the bottom piece, followed by the top. Gently press for optimal adherence. <i>Pro tip:</i> Tilt your head back for a perfect fit.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>⏳ <strong>Duration:</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Express Glow:</strong> 1-2 hours</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Maximum Results:</strong> Leave it on overnight (ensure it’s fully dry to prevent shifting).</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>💖 <strong>The Reveal:</strong> Gently remove the mask and pat the remaining essence into your skin. <i>Pro tip:</i> Use excess serum on your neck and décolleté.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggAtGlddbip_text","label":"ggAtGlddbip_text","default":"<p>Each pack comes with 4 masks. Each mask is single use. We recommend starting with 2 masks per week for a month in order to get your skin glowing fast and rejuvenated. After the first month, you can use one mask per week to maintain a healthy skin.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggvvY4AeUEN_text","label":"ggvvY4AeUEN_text","default":"<p>Use the mask 1-2 times per week for the best results. Regular use will maximize the benefits of firming, hydration, and brightening.<br><br>Leave the mask on for at least 60 minutes, but preferably 3-4 hours. The mask gradually becomes transparent, indicating that the nutrients are being absorbed.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>For the best results, use it as a sleeping mask overnight. It does not leave any residue on your pillow.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg-EoMCmSgW_text","label":"gg-EoMCmSgW_text","default":"<p>Yes, the Nifora bio-collagen mask can be used in your existing skincare routine. However, we recommend testing new products on a small patch of skin to ensure they are suitable for your skin.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggi7PaIz2q-_text","label":"ggi7PaIz2q-_text","default":"<p>Designed to be gentle on the skin. Our mask does not strip moisture or dry out, making it ideal for all skin types.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg5QaaKiVJj_text","label":"gg5QaaKiVJj_text","default":"<p>No, it is not necessary to wash your face after use. The remaining serum can be gently massaged into the skin for extra hydration.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggR3t3c7BTY_text","label":"ggR3t3c7BTY_text","default":"<p>Yes, we offer a <strong>100% money-back guarantee</strong>. If you don’t notice healthier skin, we’ll give you a full refund. Plus, enjoy our <strong>60-day risk-free guarantee</strong> for peace of mind.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggJYFQPj7dj_text","label":"ggJYFQPj7dj_text","default":"<p><strong>Processing Time:</strong> Once your order is placed, please allow 1 business day for us to process and prepare your order for shipment.<br><br><strong>Shipping Time:</strong> After your order is dispatched, it will typically take 3-5 business days to reach you, depending on your location.<br><br><strong>Tracking Information:</strong> Once your order has been shipped, you will receive an email containing your tracking number. You can use this to track your package and stay updated on its delivery&nbsp;status.</p>"}],
